# Interactive Shopping List

This is a simple interactive shopping list web application that allows users to add items, mark them as purchased, and clear the list. The list persists across page reloads using `localStorage`.

git Features

- Add items to the shopping list.
- Mark items as purchased by clicking on them.
- Clear the entire list with a single click.
- Persist the shopping list across page reloads using `localStorage`.

 Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (DOM manipulation and event handling)
- `localStorage` for persistence
